<h2>Interviewing for Research</h2>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.fivesimplesteps.com/products/interviewing-for-research" rel="external">Interviewing for Research</a></strong> by Andrew Travers was one that I really wanted to get into when I first started reading the 5 Simple Steps books as it’s one that I can directly start using the ideas from when talking with prospective clients – something I intend to do more and more of in the near future.</p>

<p>It gives tips on how to be confident when researching and communicating with clients and I’ll be referring back to this book, keeping it by my side when I write a new pre-proposal client questionnaire pretty soon. </p>

